      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2) is a commercially validated code with documented V&V history. A software quality plan covering version control, regression testing, and release documentation was reviewed and confirmed compliant with MRL 2 requirements. Unit test coverage exceeds 85% for the relevant solver modules.",
