      "rationale": "Code verification performed against three analytical benchmark cases: fully developed pipe flow (Hagen-Poiseuille), rotating disk flow (von Kármán), and lid-driven cavity at Re=1000. Observed order of accuracy matched theoretical second-order convergence rates within 5% tolerance for all three benchmarks.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
