      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Test sample characterization beyond what is documented under Test Conditions is scoped out at MRL 2. The blood analog fluid was prepared from certified reagents with lot-specific viscosity verification. Pump geometry was confirmed by CMM on the single test article. Statistical sampling across multiple manufactured units is not required at MRL 2 for this comparative hemolysis assessment."
